text: “cng raluk khna thi phraxngkh thrng hı mi kar ngib hlab khrxbnga phwk cea dwy khwam plxdphay cak phraxngkh læa thrng hı nalng ma kæ phwk cea cak fak fa pheux thrng chara phwk cea dwy na nan læa thrng hı hmd pi cak phwk cea sung khwam somm khxng chay txn læa pheux thi ca thrng phuk hawcı khxng phwk cea læa thrng hı thea mankhng dwy na nan”
